      <title>中国商飞在新加坡航展上抢走了空客和波音的风头</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-upstages-airbus-boeing-singapore-airshow-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司本周在新加坡航展上抢走了行业领头羊空客和波音公司的风头，在寻求国际认证和外国订单的同时，展示了其自主研发的C919和ARJ21喷气式飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-upstages-airbus-boeing-singapore-airshow-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:23:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司的可持续发展口号掩盖了对绿色未来的分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/airlines-sustainability-mantra-masks-divides-over-green-future-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，活动组织者在宣传新加坡航展时被问及今年的航空和国防盛会有何不同。 “可持续性，可持续性，可持续性，”他回答道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/airlines-sustainability-mantra-masks-divides-over-green-future-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国外长本月将在美国会见布林肯</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-foreign-minister-meet-blinken-us-this-month-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国外交部周四表示，韩国外交部长赵太烈将于 2 月 28 日访问美国，并与外长安东尼·布林肯举行会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-foreign-minister-meet-blinken-us-this-month-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 06:35:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚南部丛林大火烧毁，数千人被勒令逃离</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-ordered-flee-while-they-can-bushfire-burns-australias-south-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周四丛林大火失控，澳大利亚维多利亚州西部城镇已有两千多人被命令撤离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-ordered-flee-while-they-can-bushfire-burns-australias-south-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 06:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 认为无需为自愿发布的印度尼西亚新闻内容付费</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-says-not-required-pay-indonesia-news-content-posted-voluntarily-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Facebook 母公司 Meta Platforms 周四表示，它认为印度尼西亚新法律并不要求其向新闻出版商支付自愿在其平台上发布的内容的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-says-not-required-pay-indonesia-news-content-posted-voluntarily-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 05:35:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>驳船撞上中国广州附近的桥梁，导致车辆落水，两人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/two-killed-after-barge-hits-bridge-near-chinas-guangzhou-plunging-vehicles-water-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据中国官方媒体周四报道，一艘驳船与广州市附近中国珠江三角洲水道上的一座桥梁相撞，导致桥梁部分断裂，车辆坠入水中，造成两人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/two-killed-after-barge-hits-bridge-near-chinas-guangzhou-plunging-vehicles-water-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 05:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国调查船访问马尔代夫可能引发印度洋安全担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-visit-chinese-survey-ship-could-trigger-indian-ocean-security-concerns-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球船舶跟踪数据显示，一艘中国科考船于周四抵达马尔代夫，而就在三个月前，一艘类似的船只访问了印度洋并引发了新德里的安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-visit-chinese-survey-ship-could-trigger-indian-ocean-security-concerns-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 04:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾海岸警卫队称中国有关入侵的说法“不准确”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-coast-guard-says-chinese-claim-intrusion-inaccurate-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，一名菲律宾海岸警卫队官员称，中国同行声称一艘渔船“非法侵入”北京海域的说法“不准确”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-coast-guard-says-chinese-claim-intrusion-inaccurate-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 03:15:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南廉价航空公司 VietJet 同意购买 20 架空客 A330neo 喷气式飞机的临时协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/vietnamese-budget-carrier-vietjet-agrees-provisional-deal-20-airbus-a330neo-jets-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南廉价航空公司越捷航空周四表示，随着该航空公司扩大其长途航线网络，该公司已同意从欧洲空客公司订购 20 架 A330neo 宽体客机的临时协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/vietnamese-budget-carrier-vietjet-agrees-provisional-deal-20-airbus-a330neo-jets-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 03:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国医生因医院拒绝病人而继续抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/over-8000-south-korea-doctors-join-walkout-over-med-school-quotas-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国三家最大医院的急诊科周四处于红色警戒状态，实习医生发誓要停止工作，以抗议政府计划增加医学院招生以促进医疗保健行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/over-8000-south-korea-doctors-join-walkout-over-med-school-quotas-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 02:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
